attr.title: My Big Sister
attr.desc: My Big Sister is a game about Luzia and Sombria, two sisters who are trying to get back home after being kidnapped by strangers and Luzia takes it upon herself to ensure they both make it home.
attr.inst: The port supports both original and remastered version. Just purchase either of those and copy all game files into the gamedata folder.
attr.inst_md: The port supports both [original](https://store.steampowered.com/app/733300/My_Big_Sister/) and [remastered](https://store.steampowered.com/app/2118540/My_Big_Sister_Remastered) version. Just purchase either of those and copy all game files into the gamedata folder.
